    wah.giovann.csvhandler  

    • Uses of CSVFileFormat in wah.giovann.csvhandler

      Fields in wah.giovann.csvhandler declared as CSVFileFormat 
      Modifier and Type Field and Description
      static CSVFileFormat CSVFileFormat.DEFAULT_FORMAT
      Constant for the default CSVFileFormat instance.

      The default CSVFileFormat instance uses the COMMA_DELIMITER delimiter, the LINE_FEED_LINE_END output file line end, specifies that the input file has a header, specifies that fields with leading or trailing white space should be trimmed, and automatically determines the character encoding of the input file.
